title: november 23: doctor what?
description:
Today on the pod, Maia goes deep on the history of a doctor—or rather, thirteen doctors...the Doctor(s) Who! She discusses the origins of the cult favorite show as well as its connections to yesterday’s show. Then Maia talks about the humble beginnings of a song that will live forever. Listen to this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
